description: S96A Non-material minor amendments to reserved matters application reference H/04103/08 granted 22/12/2008 Reserved matters application seeking approval for landscaping, siting, design and external appearance in relation to phase 2a of the redevelopment of West Hendon Estate, comprising 186 residential units (159 flats in block 'L' and 20 flats and 5 terraced houses in block 'M') pursuant to condition 3 of outline planning permission W13937/04 for the redevelopment of the site approved 1 July 2008. Amendments to include window layout changes, omission of roof conservatories and rearrangement of roof garden, and amendments to balconies and changes to internal layouts including to basement car parking (Block L) and residential floors.
